  <div class="ethos_statement">
    <h15>&ldquo;Fashion is the ultimate way to express yourself. It is a creative, artistic and innovative endeavor. It is FUN and should be celebrated - it shouldn’t come at the cost to people or the environment.&rdquo;</h15>
    <p class="author">&mdash; BRITTANY HAAVALDSRUD, FOUNDER OF FJORDLIFE</p>
