    <div>
      <h16>OUR DREAM</h16>
      <p>One day we hope every choice offered is a sustainable one, but for now we are committed to collaborating with designers who have a vision for beautiful, innovative products with meaningful impact. We offer a highly curated selection of brands who are championing a new way of doing business. A place where style meets ethics —  and don’t they look good together.</p>
      <p>“We have partnered with designers who are doing such wonderful things to improve the standards of the design industry. Fjordlife allows us to not only highlight their innovative designs but also share with you the impact behind the product.” founder Brittany Haavaldsrud</p>
    </div>

  </div>

